  <summary date="2019-01-09T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Hire A Hero Act of 2019

 This bill allows small businesses a work opportunity tax credit for hiring a member of the Ready Reserve or the National Guard. The bill also makes permanent the provisions of the credit that apply to the hiring of qualified veterans and members of the Ready Reserve and National Guard.</summary>
